===Verb===
'''saada'''
# second person plural imperative of [[saatma]]; [[send]] (imperative, singular)
#:''Saada see kiri ära.'' Send this letter. 
# ''da''-infinitive of [[saama]]; to [[get]]
#: ''Tahan raha saada''. I want to get (the) money.

